In short, you can get this theme for completely FREE by downloading a few apps.How to get Getjar Gold to purchase and apply this theme:1. After downloading and installing this theme,go to  GOKeyboard menu->Theme Setting->Select Theme click Apply.2. Choose pay with Google Checkout or Free with Getjar Gold. 3. If you choose Getjar Gold, there will be several apps listed. Just download whatever apps you want until you have enough gold to purchase the theme.4.
